summary: A little Mod that increases the varity of gowable ingredients.
descriptionHtml:
Background

Unfortunaly my computer hasn't enough power to actually play Skyrim. Voice and image aren't synchron and already the first 15 minutes need at least 20 in reality. I normally play on PS4 and I just got the Legendary Edition to start modding, but now I can't test my own mods myself. :(
So I hope for some brave tester and their feedback.

What is this mod about?

This mod adds multiple ingredients to be growable at your Hearthfire houses (including ingredients from Dawnguard and Dragonborn). Also there is a new merchant in the inn of Ivarstead (as a Khajiit she should be easy to find) for ingredients in general.
Hope this became something enjoyable.
author: Diilsoszaam
